{"id":360919,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/52/47/524745.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"班固米做菜人","groupHref":"/group/zuocai","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/43/4324.jpg?r=1574965416","message":"<span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">珍珠丸子</span></span><br>糯米温水泡软<br>猪肉买肥瘦三七开的，剁馅，加入姜葱末、胡椒粉、盐、生抽调味<br>肉馅里打个鸡蛋，加适量水，顺一个方向搅拌上劲（这个超费手的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/19.gif\" smileid=\"58\" alt=\"(bgm42)\">）<br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/3b/ed/524745_CfhhY.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br>糯米沥干，然后搓丸子和蒸丸子~蒸15分钟左右就好啦<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\"><br>出锅之前撒点葱花！bling~~~<br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/3b/ed/524745_CdOtr.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">油渣炒辣椒</span></span><br>片下来的肥肉切丝拿来熬猪油了，熬出来的油渣炒炒辣椒也是极好的<br>猪油炒青菜好吃！但是长肉<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/45.gif\" smileid=\"84\" alt=\"(bgm68)\"><br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/3b/ed/524745_SdKBR.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">生炒糯米饭（伪）</span></span><br>糯米泡多了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">，于是加水蒸熟（第一回做水加得有点多）<br>再把广式腊肠切丁，香菇切丁，炒些花生米，<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">虾米</span>（家里没虾米了呜呜呜）<br>以上小料炒香，糯米饭下锅炒散~<br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">撒葱花香菜</span>（用完了）<br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/3b/ed/524745_8U8V5.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt> ","time":"2021-1-22 15:57","title":"珍珠丸子以及剩余原料的综合利用","userId":"524745","userName":"Acylation","userSign":""}